sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS: 6379/TCP<br/>Dashboard: 8265/TCP
    participant WorkerPods as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Ingress as Ingress/Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>kubeconfig auth
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create head pod, service<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create worker pods<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    HeadPod->>HeadPod: Start GCS<br/>localhost:6379<br/>Ray Protocol
    WorkerPods->>HeadPod: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP<br/>Ray Protocol

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>kubeconfig auth
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster + Job submitter pod<br/>HTTPS/6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>HeadPod: Submit job via dashboard API<br/>HTTP/8265
    HeadPod->>HeadPod: Store job metadata in GCS<br/>6379/TCP Ray Protocol
    HeadPod->>WorkerPods: Distribute tasks<br/>10001/TCP Ray Protocol
    WorkerPods-->>HeadPod: Task results<br/>Ray Protocol
    HeadPod-->>Operator: Job completion<br/>via K8s API

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 3: Ray Serve Inference
    User->>Ingress: POST /predict<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Ingress->>HeadPod: Forward to serve endpoint<br/>HTTP/8000
    HeadPod->>WorkerPods: Distribute inference<br/>Ray Protocol
    WorkerPods-->>HeadPod: Inference results
    HeadPod-->>Ingress: JSON response<br/>HTTP/8000
    Ingress-->>User: HTTPS response<br/>443/TCP

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Operator: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8080
    Operator-->>Prometheus: Operator metrics
    Prometheus->>HeadPod: Scrape Ray metrics<br/>HTTP/8265
    HeadPod-->>Prometheus: Ray cluster metrics
